2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcentre-to-offer-affordable-commodities-in-strife-hit-manipur-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F113404513.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20announced%20that%20starting%20September%2017%2C%202024%2C%20Kendriya%20Police%20Kalyan%20Bhandar%20outlets%20will%20provide%20reasonably%20priced%20commodities%20to%20Manipur%20residents.%20This%20initiative%20includes%20opening%2016%20new%20centres%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20existing%20ones%2C%20aimed%20at%20supporting%20the%20strife-hit%20region%20and%20fulfilling%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20commitment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22BHARTI%20JAIN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcentre-to-offer-affordable-commodities-in-strife-hit-manipur-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F113404513.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Top%20Cop%2C%20Health%20Officials%20Removed%20After%20Mamata%20Banerjee-Doctors%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minster%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20the%20protesting%20junior%20doctors%2C%20has%20announced%20that%20she%20had%20agreed%20to%20three%20of%20the%20five%20demands%20of%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20--%20the%20removal%20of%20two%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20health%20department%20and%20the%20Chief%20of%20Kolkata%20police.%C2%A0%20Along%20with%20it%2C%20the%20police%20chief%20of%20the%20city's%20north%20zone%20--%20where%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20the%20hospital%20where%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20young%20doctor%20took%20place%2C%20is%20located%20--%20will%20also%20be%20removed.%C2%A0%20Though%20the%20impasse%20is%20solved%2C%20the%20protest%20and%20the%20ceasework%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20till%20the%20formal%20orders%20are%20issued%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20meeting%20was%20positive.%20Am%20sure%20they%20think%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOr%20why%20else%20we%20will%20sign%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting%20and%20they%20would%20sign%20it%20too%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20said%20they%20have%20accepted%2099%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20doctors'%20demands%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they%20are%20our%20younger%20brothers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20they%20say%20they%20will%20go%20and%20discuss%20and%20then%20will%20decide%20on%20lifting%20the%20ceasework.%20But%20I%20have%20requested%20them%20to%20do%20so%2C%20citing%20the%20condition%20of%20patients%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20the%20floods%20in%20some%20of%20the%20districts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20say%20protest%20will%20continue%20till...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20capitulation%20of%20sorts.%20The%20atmosphere%20at%20the%20protest%20site%20after%20the%20doctors%20returned%20was%20festive.%20The%20junior%20doctors%20declared%20that%20the%20state's%20acceptance%20of%20their%20demands%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20victory%26quot%3B%20of%20their%2038-day%20protest.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20lifting%20the%20protest%20and%20the%20casework%2C%20that%20can%20only%20be%20done%20when%20the%20government%20delivers%2C%20they%20said.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20only%20received%20their%20verbal%20assurance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20so%2C%20their%20other%20aim%20--%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20nexus%20of%20corruption%20at%20the%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20remains%2C%20they%20said.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20also%20continue%20the%20agitation%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20health%20secretary%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20one%20of%20the%20other%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20State%20has%20promised%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20has%20accepted%20the%20demands%20for%20the%20upgrade%20in%20hospital%20infrastructure%20and%20Rs%20100%20crore%20has%20been%20earmarked%20for%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAbout%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20two%20health%20officials%20--%20the%20Director%20of%20Medical%20Education%20and%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Health%20Services%20--%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20they%20would%20be%20given%20transfers%20to%20proper%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20dishonouring%20them.%20They%20have%20not%20been%20in%20the%20post%20for%20long%20and%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong.%20But%20since%20the%20students%20said%20they%20do%20not%20have%20trust%20in%20them%2C%20we%20have%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20city%20police%20chief%20Vineet%20Goyal%20would%20be%20retained%20for%20at%20least%20the%20Durga%20puja.%20He%20had%20asked%20to%20resign%20several%20times%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20him%20to%20stay%20back%2C%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Mr%20Goyal's%20removal%20came%20in%20view%20of%20allegations%20about%20the%20police%20role%20in%20evidence%20tampering%20after%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20August%209.%20This%20was%20commented%20on%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20or%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20has%20arrested%20the%20hospital's%20former%20Principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20and%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bfifth%20and%20final%20invitation%20for%20talks%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20announcement%20took%20place%20close%20to%20midnight%2C%20after%20a%20two-hour%20meeting%20with%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20and%20another%202.5%20hours%20to%20type%20out%20the%20minutes%20of%20the%20meeting.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%20the%20state%20government%20had%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfifth%20and%20final%20invitation%20for%20talks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20junior%20doctors%20had%20come%20to%20the%20table%20after%20two%20failed%20attempts%20at%20talks%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Escorted%20by%20a%20pilot%20police%20vehicle%2C%20around%2030%20doctors%20had%20arrived%20at%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20home%20at%206.20%20pm.%20The%20meeting%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20begin%C2%A0%20at%205%20pm%2C%20finally%20started%20around%207%20pm%20and%20ended%20around%209%20pm%2C%20after%20which%20the%20process%20to%20finalise%20the%20minutes%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20had%20taken%20their%20own%20stenographers%20to%20record%20the%20minutes.%20The%20document%20was%20signed%20by%2040%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impasse%20over%20the%20doctors'%20demand%20for%20justice%20for%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20medic%20has%20been%20on%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ordered%20that%20the%20doctors%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20ceasework%20and%20get%20back%20to%20patient%20care%2C%20which%20is%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20had%20ended%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20ceasework%2C%20as%20doctors%20across%20India%20had%20stood%20up%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20the%20protesters.%20But%20Bengal%20doctors%20had%20refused%2C%20doubling%20down%20with%20the%20protests%20as%20the%20common%20people%20kept%20up%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rape-murder%20That%20shocked%20the%20country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2031-year%3Dold%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20hospital%20on%20August%209.%20Her%20partially%20clothed%20body%20was%20found%20at%20the%20hospital's%20seminar%20room%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20suspect%2C%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20is%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20who%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20police%20outpost%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20had%20access%20to%20all%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20investigation%20had%20left%20too%20many%20questions%20unanswered%20--%20including%20the%20various%20distorted%20versions%20told%20to%20the%20parents%20one%20of%20which%20was%20the%20claim%20that%20their%20daughter%20has%20died%20by%20suicide.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20were%20also%20allegations%20that%20the%20police%20had%20forced%20the%20cremation%20despite%20the%20parents'%20unwillingness%20and%20one%20officer%20had%20even%20offered%20them%20money%20to%20bury%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20the%20construction%20near%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20mob%20attack%20on%20the%20protesters%20at%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2015%20and%20the%20transfer%20of%20Sandip%20Ghosh%20to%20a%20top%20hospital%20hours%20after%20he%20submitted%20his%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20questioned%20why%20the%20former%20principal%20had%20not%20file%20a%20complaint%20for%20a%20timely%20First%20Information%20Report%2C%20the%20lapses%20in%20postmortem%20report%20and%20the%20associated%20papers.%20The%20case%20was%20handed%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20first%20arrested%20Ghosh%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20parallel%20corruption%20case%20they%20are%20investigating%20and%20then%20for%20alleged%20evidence%20tampering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sequence%20of%20events%20led%20to%20spiralling%20protests%20that%20spread%20across%20the%20country%2C%20already%20outraged%20over%20the%20shocking%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726516320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc85d5b7_mamata-banerjee_625x300_16_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-police-commissioner-2-health-department-officers-r