n't%20hint%20at%20an%20upgrade%20super%20cycle.%3Cp%3EApple%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20fans%20bought%20an%20estimated%2037%20million%20new%20iPhone%2016s%20during%20the%20first%20weekend%20of%20pre-orders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20about%2012.7%25%20lower%20than%20last%20year's%20iPhone%2015%20series%20first-weekend%20sales%2C%20one%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20had%20speculated%20the%2016%2C%20featuring%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20would%20drive%20a%20major%20upgrade%20cycle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016's%20first%20weekend%20on%20sale%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20matching%20up%20with%20the%20monthslong%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20Apple's%20first%20iPhone%20%26quot%3Bbuilt%20from%20the%20ground%20up%26quot%3B%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-just-threw-down-gauntlet-in-ai-wars-intelligence-wwdc-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20tech%20giant's%20AI%20plans%20as%20they%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20spend%20heavily%20to%20get%20ahead%20in%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIPhone%20sales%20have%20slipped%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-aapl-stock-quarterly-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20months%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20some%20analysts%20have%20predicted%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-event-iphone-16-announcement-live-updates-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20outfitted%20with%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20of%20Apple%20Intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20the%20smartphone%20that%20would%20drive%20a%20massive%20upgrade%20cycle.%