ed%20felon%20and%20possession%20of%20a%20firearm%20with%20an%20obliterated%20serial%20number.%20The%20charges%20carry%20a%20maximum%20prison%20sentence%20of%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FBI%20affidavit%20filed%20with%20the%20suspect's%20criminal%20complaint%20gives%20the%20most%20complete%20narrative%20yet%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20second%20attempt%20in%20two%20months%20on%20the%20former%20president's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20was%20spotted%20at%201%3A31%20p.m.%20on%20Sunday%20by%20a%20Secret%20Service%20agent%20from%20Trump's%20security%20detail%2C%20the%20affidavit%20released%20Monday%20says.%20The%20unnamed%20agent%20was%20walking%20the%20golf%20course's%20perimeter%20and%20%26quot%3Bsaw%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20rifle%20poking%20out%20of%20the%20tree%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agent%20fired%20his%2Fher%20service%20weapon%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20rifle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20adds.%20%26quot%3BA%20witness%20saw%20a%20male%2C%20later%20identified%20as%20Routh%2C%20fleeing%20the%20area%20of%20the%20tree%20line%20and%20entering%20a%20Nissan%20sport%20utility%20vehicle.%20The%20witness%20then%20observed%20the%20Nissan%20leave%20the%20area%20at%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20left%20behind%20%26quot%3Ba%20digital%20camera%2C%20two%20(2)%20bags%2C%20including%20a%20backpack%2C%20a%20loaded%20SKS-style%2C%207.62%C3%9739%20caliber%20rifle%20with%20a%20scope%2C%20and%20a%20black%20plastic%20bag%20containing%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rifle's%20serial%20number%20%26quot%3Bwas%20obliterated%20and%20unreadable%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20has%20a%202002%20conviction%20from%20Greensboro%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20for%20%26quot%3Bpossession%20of%20a%20weapon%20of%20mass%20death%20and%20destruction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20convicted%20in%202010%20in%20North%20Carolina%20of%20multiple%20counts%20of%20possession%20of%20stolen%20goods%2C%20the%20affidavit%20says%2C%20and%20is%20therefore%20not%20allowed%20to%20possess%20a%20firearm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20cellphone%20number%20and%20records%20were%20quickly%20retrieved%20thanks%20to%20his%20own%20Facebook%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20had%20posted%20his%20phone%20number%20in%20a%20message%20sent%20from%20the%20tree%20line%20at%201%3A59%20a.m.%20Sunday%2C%20directing%20his%20followers%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20him%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgents%20requested%20T-Mobile%2C%20on%20an%20emergency%20basis%2C%20to%20provide%20law%20enforcement%20with%20information%20pertaining%20to%20Routh's%20mobile%20phone%20usage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20records%20indicated%20that%20Routh's%20mobile%20phone%20was%20located%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20area%20along%20the%20tree%20line%20described%20above%20from%20approximately%201%3A59%20a.m.%20until%20approximately%201%3A31%20p.m.%20on%20September%2015%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20is%20due%20to%20be%20back%20at%20federal%20court%20in%20West%20Palm%20Beach%20in%20two%20weeks%20to%20be%20arraigned%20on%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-apparent-assassination-attempt-suspect-stake-out-golf-club-complaint-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726508406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e86a56d17aa3c7b2b30f4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-apparent-assassination-attempt-suspect-stake-out-golf-club-complaint-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20say%20the%20suspect's%20cellphone%20was%20at%20Trump