ter%2C%20who%20has%20also%20worked%20in%20Kannada%20and%20Hindi%20films%2C%20assaulted%20multiple%20times%2C%20including%20once%20at%20a%20Mumbai%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20are%20trying%20to%20contact%20the%20woman%20to%20record%20a%20detailed%20statement%2C%20but%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bunreachable%26quot%3B%20at%20this%20time%2C%20Chief%20Inspector%20Krishna%20Reddy%20told%20reporters%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20she%20met%20Master%20at%20an%20event%20in%202017.%20Two%20years%20later%20he%20offered%20her%20a%20job%20as%20an%20assistant%20choreographer%2C%20which%20she%20accepted.%20The%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20took%20place%20after%20that%20-%20at%20a%20hotel%20Master%20and%20she%2C%20and%20other%20dancers%2C%20were%20staying%20in%20during%20a%20Mumbai%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20she%20said%20Jani%20Master%20and%20two%20other%20male%20assistants%20had%20travelled%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20she%20would%20normally%20have%20been%20accompanied%20by%20her%20mother%2C%20but%20was%20not%20this%20time%20since%20there%20tickets%20were%20not%20available.%20She%20also%20claimed%20Master%20threatened%20her%20if%20she%20told%20anyone%20of%20the%20assault%20and%20continued%20to%20harass%20her%20during%20shoots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%20he%20even%20forced%20her%20to%20convert%20to%20his%20religion%20and%20'marry'%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20months%20Master%20would%20apparently%20frequently%20summon%20her%20to%20his%20cabin%20and%20sexually%20assault%20her%2C%20threatening%20to%20ruin%20her%20career%20if%20she%20did%20not%20comply%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20also%20alleged%20Master%20would%20show%20up%20at%20her%20home%20some%20nights%20and%2C%20on%20one%20occasion%2C%20his%20wife%20(he%20was%20already%20married)%20and%20Master%20barged%20into%20her%20room%20and%20slapped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20acting%20swiftly%20to%20evade%20political%20backlash%2C%20actor-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20(a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20at%20the%20centre)%20has%20ordered%20Master%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20its%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaster%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20has%20told%20local%20media%20he%20has%20not%20been%20expelled%2C%20and%20has%20no%20issues%20with%20the%20party%20leadership's%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20coalition%20partner%20Jana%20Sena%20has%20decided%20to%20keep%20Jani%20Master%20away%20from%20party%20activities.%20The%20party%20took%20the%20decision%20on%20Monday%20after%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20Jani%20Master%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20IANS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV.%20Ajay%20Kumar%2C%20head%2C%20Conflict%20Management%2C%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20decision%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20comes%20amid%20over%20churn%20in%20the%20Kerala%20movie%20business%20after%20the%20release%20of%20a%20partly%20redacted%20judicial%20committee%20report%20triggered%20an%20avalanche%20of%20sex%20assault%20allegations%20against%20senior%20actors%20and%20filmmakers.%20That%20list%20includes%20M%20Mukesh%20-%20an%20MLA%20with%20Kerala's%20ruling%20CPIM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20actors%20and%20directors%20like%20Nivin%20Pauly%2C%20Jayasurya%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20and%20Siddique%20all%20face%20multiple%20charges%20of%20assault%20and%2For%20rape%2C%20and%20are%20being%20investigated%20by%20a%20special%20police%20team%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government.%20They%20have%20all%20denied%20the%20claims%20and%20labelled%20them%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmalayalam-actor-sowmya-ndtv-interview-amid-m