7%20pm%20and%20ended%20around%209%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%2C%20though%2C%20are%20yet%20to%20emerge%20from%20the%20Chief%20Ministers'%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20earlier%20meetings%20--%20the%20last%20one%20attempted%20on%20Saturday%20--%20had%20fallen%20though%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20could%20not%20come%20to%20a%20consensus%20on%20whether%20the%20proceedings%20should%20be%20live%20transmitted%20or%20videographed%2C%20with%20the%20video%20handed%20to%20the%20doctors%20right%20after%20it%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20reached%20the%20venue%20but%20left%20without%20sitting%20down%20at%20the%20proverbial%20table.%20On%20the%20first%20occasion%2C%20images%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20sitting%20in%20an%20empty%20meeting%20hall%20of%20the%20state%20secretariat%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20doctors'%20delegation%2C%20had%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20did%20Saturday's%20cellphone%20videos%20of%20her%20asking%20the%20doctors%20to%20come%20inside%20her%20Kalighat%20home%20and%20have%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20at%20least%20even%20if%20they%20were%20unwilling%20to%20join%20discussions.%20The%20doctors%20had%20refused%2C%20saying%20they%20want%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20most%20of%20the%20conditions%20have%20been%20laid%20down%20in%20writing%20ahead%20of%20the%20meet%2C%20negating%20any%20chance%20of%20last-minute%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20taken%20their%20own%20stenographers%20who%20would%20record%20the%20minutes%20and%20the%20document%20will%20be%20signed%20by%20everyone%20present.%20The%20government%20will%20also%20have%20a%20video%20recording.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20also%20stipulated%20that%20they%20give%20their%20response%20to%20whatever%20the%20government%20had%20to%20say%20after%20going%20back%20to%20the%20protest%20site%20and%20discussing%20it%20with%20the%20others.%20They%20have%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20will%20not%20give%20up%20on%20their%20five-point%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20want%20the%20issue%20to%20be%20resolved%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20any%20form%20of%20compromise%20on%20our%20five%20demands.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20the%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20all%20the%20issues%20with%20an%20open%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20protesters%20who%20is%20also%20participating%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impasse%20over%20the%20doctors'%20demand%20for%20justice%20for%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20medic%20has%20been%20on%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ordered%20that%20the%20doctors%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20ceasework%20and%20get%20back%20to%20patient%20care%2C%20which%20is%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20had%20ended%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20ceasework%2C%20as%20doctors%20across%20India%20had%20stood%20up%20to%20show%20solidarity%20with%20the%20protesters.%20But%20Bengal%20doctors%20had%20refused%2C%20doubling%20down%20with%20the%20protests%20as%20the%20common%20people%20kept%20up%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20first%20time%20the%20talks%20fell%20through%20even%20before%20they%20started%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%C2%A0%20had%20assured%20doctors%20that%20no%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20them%2C%20and%20that%20the%20government%20is%20always%20ready%20for%20a%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%2C%20she%20said%2C%20had%20taken%20action%20in%20similar%20circumstances.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20have%20ESMA%20(Essential%20Services%20Maintenance%20Act).%20But%20I%20will%20not%20do%20that.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20supporter%20of%20Emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%20But%20there%20was%20also%20a%20warning%20--%20she%20said%20she%20is%20also%20answerable%20to%20the%20families%20that%20lose%20their%20loved%20ones%20because%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20doctors%20in%20hospitals.%20The%20government%20had%20claimed%20that%20till%20then%2C%20that%20figured%20hovered%20around%20the%20late%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20had%20rubbished%20the%20allegation%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20while%20the%20state%20had%20nearly%20one%20lakh%20registered%20doctors%2C%20the%20number%20of%20junior%20doctors%20was%20around%204%2C500%20and%20their%20absence%20cannot%20cause%20a%20breakdown%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726502760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F18p5j2uo_doctor-protest_625x300_11_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-protesting-doctors-finally-meet-to-end-impasse-6578971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20protesting%20junior%20doctors%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20after%20two%20failed%20attempts%20at%20talks%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20held%20a%20two-hour%20discussion%20with%20her%20at%20her%20Kalighat%20residence%20this%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-protesting-doctors-finally-meet-to-end-impasse-6578971%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Katrina%20wanted%20to%20tie%20Rakhi%20to%20Akshay-Arjun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726502669000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113401822%2Cimgsize-46710.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fdid-you-know%2Fdid-you-know-katrina-kaif-once-wanted-to-tie-rakhi-to-akshay-kumar-and-arjun-kapoor-their-reactions-were-priceless%2Farticleshow%2F113401821.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113401821.cms