20the%20largest%20government%20hospital%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20stopped%20open-heart%20surgeries%20for%20four%20months%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20reagents.%20This%20has%20left%20many%20economically%20weaker%20patients%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Dr%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20Hospital%20in%20huge%20trouble%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20seek%20expensive%20private%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReagents%2C%20which%20are%20used%20in%20tests%20before%20and%20during%20the%20surgery%2C%20are%20in%20short%20supply%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Raipur%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20impoverished%20states%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20who%20depend%20on%20government%20healthcare%20are%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20this%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadan%20Gopal%2C%20a%20security%20guard%20from%20Korba%20district%2C%20has%20been%20running%20from%20one%20hospital%20to%20another%20for%20his%20surgery.%20His%20family%20eventually%20took%20loans%20to%20treat%20him%20at%20a%20private%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20referred%20to%20Raipur%20AIIMS%2C%20and%20then%20further%20referred%20to%20Ambedkar%20Hospital.%20But%20we%20were%20told%20that%20surgeries%20are%20on%20hold%20there.%20After%20another%20visit%20to%20AIIMS%2C%20we%20were%20told%20the%20waiting%20period%20was%20too%20long%20for%20my%20father's%20condition%2C%20so%20we%20are%20now%20struggling%20to%20arrange%20funds%20for%20private%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gopal's%20son%20Ankush%20Kumar%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospital%20performs%2030-40%20heart%20surgeries%20a%20month%2C%20but%20the%20shortage%20of%20reagents%20in%20the%20advanced%20cardiac%20department%20has%20been%20crippling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20the%20reagent%2C%20the%20heart-lung%20machine%2C%20which%20keeps%20the%20patient%20alive%20during%20the%20procedure%2C%20cannot%20be%20properly%20monito