iamond%20reaches%20a%20person%20who%20does%20not%20know%20its%20worth%2C%20he%20destroys%20it.%20I%20don't%20say%20it%20myself%20that%20Yograj%20Singh%20is%20a%20%C2%A0great%20character%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuvraj%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F456-yuvraj-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20it%2C%20'there%20is%20magic%20in%20my%20dad's%20hand%2C%20he%20made%20me%20what%20I%20am.'%20Earlier%2C%20I%20was%20abused%20'Hitler%2C%20Dragon%20Singh%2C%20I%20hate%20my%20father'.%20Everybody%20hated%20me%20in%20my%20home.%20My%20relatives%20said%2C%20I%20should%20not%20have%20been%20a%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20Yograj%20Singh%20replied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20walked%20his%20path.%20And%20by%20God's%20Grace%20you%20got%20Yuvraj%20Singh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726496580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F6nau6leg_arjun-tendulkar_625x300_25_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F9-87-in-26-3-overs-arjun-tendulkar-turns-heads-with-terrific-display-for-this-team-6579306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arjun%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20will%20turn%2025%20next%20week%2C%20has%20so%20far%20played%2049%20competitive%20games%20across%20three%20formats%20at%20senior%20level%20and%20picked%2068%20wickets%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2F9-87-in-26-3-overs-arjun-tendulkar-turns-heads-with-terrific-display-for-this-team-6579306%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFilled%20With%20Hate%2C%20Defaming%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Amid%20Row%20Over%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Sikh%20Jab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20said%20%26quo