0the%20second%20season%20is%20after%20a%20stellar%20first%20season.%20If%20sky-rocketing%20expectations%20are%20one%20aspect%20of%20it%2C%20the%20other%20part%20comprises%20of%20opposition's%20familiarity%20with%20his%20game%20and%20enough%20on-ground%20material%20available%20for%20dissection.%20As%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20eyes%20to%20beat%20second%20season%20blues%2C%20he%20can%20consider%20himself%20lucky%20that%20that%20he%20gets%20to%20face%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20the%20best%20in%20the%20business%20that%20you%20want%20to%20face%20before%20real%20action%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Monday's%20net%20session%2C%20Bumrah%20repeatedly%20made%20short%20work%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20youngster%20often%20sending%20his%20off-stump%20cart-wheeling%20for%20fun.%20Jaiswal%20would%20hope%20that%20sketchy%20form%20in%20the%20nets%20wouldn't%20be%20carried%20in%20the%20opening%20Test%20against%20Bangladesh%20starting%20here%20on%20September%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2010%20Tests%20this%20season%2C%20Jaiswal%20coming%20in%20with%20heady%20reputation%20as%20one%20of%20the%20future%20megastar%20in%20making%20having%20scored%201000%20plus%20runs%20in%20his%20first%209%20Tests%20with%20700%20plus%20coming%20against%20England%20in%20a%20single%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Jaiswal's%20critics%20will%20certainly%20point%20out%20that%20in%20those%20nine%20games%2C%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20against%20South%20Africa%20on%20bouncy%20tracks%20of%20Centurion%20and%20Newlands%20(Cape%20Town)%20where%20he%20didn't%20exactly%20comfortable%20against%20pace%20and%20bounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20England%20series%20where%20he%20