%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20being%20gleeful%2C%20having%20climbed%20a%20tree.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20teachers%2C%20says%20Nehal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20with%20kids%20below%20three%2C%20she%20says%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20go%20with%20the%20flow.%20You%20will%20experience%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20misses%20and%20hits.%20Take%20everything%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20part%20of%20the%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20some%20words%20of%20advice%20to%20parents%20in%20an%20increasingly%20competitive%20world%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20parenting%20as%20a%20pressure.%20Slow%20down.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20not%20be%20busy%20all%20the%20time.%20Let%20your%20children%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20beyond%20gadgets%20and%20video%20games.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelling%20teaches%20both%20you%20and%20your%20children%20mindfulness%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20present.%20It%20helps%20you%20shed%20your%20ego%20as%20you%20come%20to%20realise%20that%20you%20are%20not%20greater%20than%20nature.%20No%20school%20can%20provide%20the%20lessons%20that%20nature%20offers.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20fosters%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community%20bound%20by%20a%20shared%20love%20for%20the%20natural%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nehal%20Shah%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726491246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnehal-shah-1726490018.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nehal%20Shah%2C%20an%20avid%20traveller%2C%20began%20taking%20her%20son%20on%20her%20adventures%20and%20saw%20the%20value%20of%20outdoor%20experiences%20for%20families.%20Recognising%20the%20importance%20of%20nature-based%20experiences%20for%20children%2C%20she%20founded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russians%20Urged%20To%20Have%20Sex%20During%20Work%20Breaks%20Amid%20Declining%20Birth%20Rate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20reportedly%20encouraged%20Russians%20to%20engage%20in%20intimate%20relations%20during%20lunch%20and%20coffee%20breaks%20at%20work%20to%20address%20the%20country's%20declining%20birth%20rate.%20The%20initiative%20comes%20as%20Russia's%20fertility%20rate%2C%20currently%20at%20about%201.5%20children%20per%20woman%2C%20falls%20significantly%20below%20the%202.1%20rate%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20stable%20population%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F09%2F15%2Fvladimir-putin-demands-russians-sex-work-fall-birth-rate-21608541%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Additionally%2C%20over%20a%20million%2C%20primarily%20younger%20Russians%2C%20have%20left%20the%20country%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Ukraine%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Dr%20Yevgeny%20Shestopalov%20emphasised%20that%20being%20too%20busy%20at%20work%20is%20not%20a%20valid%20excuse%20for%20avoiding%20procreation.%20He%20suggested%20that%20people%20could%20take%20advantage%20of%20breaks%20to%20focus%20on%20expanding%20their%20families%2C%20noting%20that%20''life%20flies%20by%20too%20quickly.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20reporter%20asked%20him%20how%20people%20working%2012%20to%2014%20hours%20a%20day%20would%20find%20time%20to%20have%20children%2C%20he%20responded%20by%20suggesting%20they%20could%20use%20their%20break%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Putin%20has%20insisted%2C%20''The%20preservation%20of%20the%20Russian%20people%20is%20our%20highest%20national%20priority.%20The%20fate%20of%20Russia....depends%20on%20how%20many%20of%20us%20there%20will%20be.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20national%20importance.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Russia's%20birth%20rate%20has%20hit%20its%20lowest%20point%20since%201999%2C%20with%20the%20number%20of%20live%20births%20in%20June%20falling%20below%20100%2C000.%20This%20drastic%20drop%20has%20raised%20concerns%20in%20Moscow%20about%20a%20severe%20population%20decline.%20According%20to%20Rosstat%2C%20Russia's%20governmental%20statistics%20agency%2C%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20decrease%20in%20births%2C%20with%2016%2C000%20fewer%20children%20born%20between%20January%20and%20June%202024%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euronews.com%2F2024%2F09%2F10%2Frussias-birth-rate-drops-to-its-lowest-in-a-quarter-century-data-shows%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEuro%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decline%20is%20further%20exacerbated%20by%20an%2018%25%20increase%20in%20population%20decline%2C%20with%2049%2C000%20more%20deaths%20recorded%20in%202024%20than%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin's%20efforts%20to%20boost%20Russia's%20declining%20birth%20rate%20have%20led%20to%20a%20series%20of%20measures%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFree%20fertility%20checks%3A%20Women%20in%20Moscow%2C%20aged%2018-40%2C%20are%20encouraged%20to%20undergo%20free%20fertility%20assessments%20to%20evaluate%20their%20%26quot%3Breproductive%20potential%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEmployer%20coercion%3A%20MP%20Tatyana%20Butskaya%20has%20proposed%20a%20plan%20to%20pressure%20employers%20into%20encouraging%20their%20female%20employees%20to%20have%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIncentives%3A%C2%A0Chelyabinsk%20region%20is%20offering%C2%A08%2C500%20pounds%C2%A0to%20female%20students%20under%2024%20for%20their%20first%20child's%20birth%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERestricting%20abortion%3A%20Access%20to%20abortion%20across%20the%20country%20is%20being%20blocked%20as%20public%20figures%20and%20churchmen%20claim%20women's%20duty%20is%20to%20give%20birth%20and%20raise%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDivorce%20fees%3A%C2%A0Fees%20for%20divorce%20have%20been%20increased%20to%20discourage%20separation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitician%20Anna%20Kuznetsova%20has%20also%20demanded%20women%20start%20giving%20birth%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20She%20said%3A%20''You%20should%20start%20giving%20birth%20at%2019-20%20years%20old.%20Then%2C%20statistically%2C%20the%20family%20will%20be%20able%20to%20have%20three%2C%20four%2C%20or%20more%20children.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20critics%20argue%20these%20policies%20undermine%20individual%20autonomy%2C%20particularly%20for%20women%2C%20and%20may%20have%20unintended%20consequences%20on%20