0question.%20As%20Zavi%20Paphino%20rattles%20off%20the%20names%20of%20the%20bones%2C%20his%20confidence%20is%20unmistakable.%20The%20professor%E2%80%99s%20nod%20signals%20he%20has%20got%20the%20answer%20right.%20This%20thrills%20Zavi%2C%20a%20first-year%20MBBS%20student%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F214219%2Fladakh-first-surgeon-tsering-norbu-real-hero-health-inspiring-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20aspiring%20surgeon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20the%20day%20he%20secured%20admission%20into%20the%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20in%20Kohima%2C%20Nagaland.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20moment%20had%20been%20a%20lifetime%20in%20the%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Zavi%20first%20dreamt%20of%20becoming%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20resigned%20himself%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20would%20%E2%80%94%20like%20numerous%20other%20Nagaland%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20have%20to%20move%20out%20of%20his%20home%20state%20to%20pursue%20his%20medical%20studies.%20The%20competition%20is%20fierce.%20Before%20the%20NIMSR%20was%20instated%2C%20the%20youth%20of%20Nagaland%20would%20hustle%20to%20secure%20admission%20to%20one%20of%20the%2063%20seats%20reserved%20for%20them%20in%20medical%20colleges%20across%20India.%20These%20included%2021%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20states%20of%20Manipur%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20and%20Tripura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-college-1726051697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Soumya%20Chakraborty%20at%20her%20desk%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-college-1726051697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.