%3Emulga%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(gun%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%2C%20and%20other%20products%20were%20also%20introduced.%20Reshma%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20then%20created%20a%20platform%20to%20sell%20these%20nostalgic%20products%2C%20naming%20it%20%E2%80%98Tocco%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98The%20Orange%20Candy%20Co%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20sense%20because%2C%20for%20Reshma%2C%20the%20ultimate%20symbol%20of%20nostalgia%20was%20the%20orange%20candies%20she%20shared%20with%20her%20sister%20during%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tocco%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20pack%20this%20childhood%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20box%20for%20other%20people%20to%20enjoy.%20In%20late%202022%2C%20she%20quit%20her%20job%20to%20fully%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20onboarding%20the%20first%20two%20chefs%2C%20Reshma%20brought%20in%20more%2C%20expanding%20the%20platform%20to%20include%20over%2016%20chefs%20from%20different%20cities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20They%20offer%20snacks%20like%20banana%20chips%2C%20jackfruit%20chips%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshankarpali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sweet%20snack)%3Cem%3E%2C%20masalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20sambar%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%20podi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powder)%2C%20pickles%20like%20prawn%2C%20cut%20mango%2C%20homemade%20curd%20chilli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuli%20inji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ginger%20pickle)%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2058-year-old%20Uma%20Suresh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20cooking%20since%20she%20was%20in%20Class%206%2C%20Tocco%20has%20given%20new%20meaning%20to%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CCooking%20is%20my%20passion.%20I%20would%20always%20pack%20some%20pickles%20for%20anyone%20who%20came%20home.%20I%20always%20dreamed%20of%20running%20a%20business%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20daughters%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20made%20a%20name%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Uma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC89D7o5SBhy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20MeenGurry%20Memories%20(%40meengurry_memories)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Uma%20and%20her%20sister%20Lakshmi%20embarked%20on%20trips%20to%20Dubai%20and%20Goa%20using%20their%20own%20earnings!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavana%20Shah%2C%2051%2C%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20makes%20snacks%20and%20starters%20and%20runs%20cooking%20classes%2C%20says%20Tocco%20has%20given%20her%20a%20renewed%20sense%20of%20vigour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20is%20very%20important%20for%20women%20over%2050%2C%20especially%20when%20going%20through%20menopause.%20Dealing%20with%20the%20hot%20flashes%20and%20mood%20swings%20is%20easier%20when%20we%20are%20busy.%20While%20I%20had%20regular%20customers%20in%20Vile%20Parle%2C%20Tocco%20has%20helped%20people%20across%20the%20country%20discover%20who%20I%20am.%20I%20thank%20Reshma%20for%20giving%20me%20a%20new%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhavana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20also%20offers%20flexibility%20to%20chefs%20like%20Bhavana%2C%20who%20occasionally%20travels%20abroad%20to%20visit%20her%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20Tocco%20assists%20with%20branding%20and%20marketing%2C%20which%20are%20major%20challenges%20in%20establishing%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20crore!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reshma%2C%20the%20team%20at%20Tocco%20ensures%20that%20all%20products%20are%20homemade%2C%20carefully%20crafted%20in%20small%20batches%2C%20and%20preservative-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20a%20chef%20at%20Tocco%2C%20one%20must%20apply%20on%20the%20website.%20After%20an%20initial%20call%2C%20the%20top%20three%20dishes%20of%20the%20chef%20are%20discussed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dishes%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349127%2Fwoman-startup-bakery-cakelicious-cake-tubs-in-kolkata-fatema-barodawala-single-mother-business-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%2C%20preservative%20free%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20at%20least%2030%20days.%20They%20should%20be%20regional%20or%20local%20specialities.%20We%20ask%20them%20for%20an%20ingredient%20list%20and%20take%20the%20next%20steps%20based%20on%20that.%20No%20palm%20oil%20is%20allowed.%20Chefs%20send%20samples%20of%20their%20dishes%2C%20which%20a%20focus%20group%20tastes.%20We%20suggest%20changes%2C%20and%20if%20satisfied%2C%20we%20begin%20the%20onboarding%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reshma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tips%20to%20start%20a%20business%20from%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FTocco-graphic-1726034371-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20chefs%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20brand%20of%20their%20own%2C%20Tocco%20helps%20them%20with%20the%20packaging%2C%20branding%2C%20and%20labelling.%20They%20inspect%20their%20kitchens%2C%20train%20them%2C%20and%20even%20help%20with%20getting%20an%20FSSAI%20certification%2C%20in%20case%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Tocco%20receives%20an%20order%2C%20they%20send%20it%20to%20the%20chef%2C%20who%20makes%20the%20dish%20to%20order%20and%20ships%20it.%20The%20platform%20handles%20order%20management%2C%20packing%2C%20shipping%2C%20and%20customer%20care.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20provide%20access%20to%20healthy%2C%20homemade%20food%20for%20busy%20people.%20The%20biggest%20motivation%20is%20seeing%20chefs%20like%20my%20mother%20live%20an%20independent%20life%20thanks%20to%20their%20earnings.%20Many%20of%20them%20would%20not%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20their%20products%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20opportunity%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Tocco%20processes%20over%201%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%20They%20plan%20to%20onboard%20more%20chefs%20and%20expand%20their%20operations.%20Reshma%20divides%20her%20time%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Kochi%2C%20where%20she%20has%20set%20up%20a%20facility%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20banana%20chips%2C%20one%20of%20their%20best%20selling%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Bhavana%20baking%20nankhatai.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-500x648.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-232x300.jpeg%20232w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165-150x194.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fchef-bhavana-1726038165.jpeg%20742w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Bhavana%20baking%20%3Cem%3Enankhatai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reshma%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20is%20convincing%20customers%20to%20wait%20for%20their%20orders.%20%E2%80%9COur%20USP%20is%20that%20everything%20is%20made%20in%20small%20batches.%20With%20the%20rise%20of%20quick%20commerce%2C%20customers%20sometimes%20expect%20next-day%20delivery%2C%20which%20becomes%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETocco%20is%20inspiring%20confidence%20in%20people%20across%20age%20groups%2C%20especially%20in%20their%2050s%20