h-quality%20ingredients%20and%20the%20use%20of%20gloves%20and%20masks.%20We%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20any%20excess%20requirements%20that%20are%20needed%20for%20the%20hygiene%20criteria%20to%20be%20met.%20This%20also%20includes%20renovating%20their%20facilities%20free%20of%20charge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanu%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExtending%20a%20hand%20of%20help%20to%20the%20locals%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pain%20point%20that%20was%20anticipated%20when%20they%20set%20out%20to%20launch%20Fulva%20was%20that%20it%20would%20be%20tough%20to%20break%20the%20sentimental%20mindset%20people%20associated%20with%20while%20purchasing%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20local%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShabas%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCustomers%20see%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F129745%2Ffood-history-indian-sweets-mysore-pak-agra-petha%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20nostalgic%20treat%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20present%20it%20in%20a%20modern%20way%20that%20everyone%20would%20accept.%E2%80%9D%20But%2C%20all%20doubts%20were%20erased%20when%20the%20friends%E2%80%99%20first%20box%20featuring%2024%20premium%20variations%20of%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20an%20instant%20hit%20and%20the%20order%20tally%20crossed%20300%20right%20in%20the%20first%20month%20of%20starting%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20delivers%20to%20foreign%20shores%20as%20well%20and%20has%20shipped%20its%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20the%20UK%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Germany%20and%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-4-1725529102.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20of%20homemakers